83_Remote%20Campus.svg" alt="" class="product__hero-bg-img"/></div><div class="section"><div class="container"><div class="product__badge"><img src="https://assets.website-files.com/5e966657bfb4cd1e103e404b/5ec64828d0db4bd7db8adb7a_remote%20badge%20icon.svg" alt="" class="product__badge-icon"/><div class="h3">Remote Campus</div></div><div class="product__intro-heading-wrapper wide"><h2 class="text-dark-blue">Continuity and community<span class="em-med block">for students who are scattered</span></h2><div class="product__intro-subhead">Remote Campus is designed to support the transition from on-campus to remote student experience. Simply said, it brings the campus to your students&#x27; smartphones, and supports them with the tools and resources they need, no matter where they are. In this ‘new normal’, Remote Campus creates a new, rich and tailored remote campus experience that keeps students engaged and on track.</div></div></div></div><div class="section product__features-section"><div class="container"><div class="row feature-row"><div class="col col-5 col-m-6 col-sm-10 col-xs-12"><div class="feature-block"><img src="https://assets.website-files.com/5e966657bfb4cd1e103e404b/5ed197ce57be3a5e41deae5d_user_chat.svg" alt="" class="feature-icon"/><h3 class="feature-heading">Remote campus community</h3><div class="feature-block-indent"><p>At a time when students are suddenly isolated and scattered, bringing back a sense of community and togetherness is critical. Remote Campus enables rich human interactions and reconnects students to their support system.</p></div></div></div><div class="col col-5 col-m-6 col-sm-12"><div class="feature-img-wrapper"><img src="https://assets.website-files.com/5e966657bfb4cd1e103e404b/5edefa10ce4c85fb1217d2e1_remote%201.png" srcset="https://assets.website-files.com/5e966657bfb4cd1e103e404b/5edefa10ce4c85fb1217d2e1_remote%201-p-500.png 500w, https://assets.website-files.com/5e966657bfb4cd1e103e404b/5edefa10ce4c85fb1217d2e1_remote%201.png 9