ime.</p></div></div></div><div class="col col-5 col-m-6 col-sm-12"><div class="feature-img-wrapper"><img src="https://assets.website-files.com/5e966657bfb4cd1e103e404b/5edefa0bdc17aa12fc7cf77f_remote%203.png" srcset="https://assets.website-files.com/5e966657bfb4cd1e103e404b/5edefa0bdc17aa12fc7cf77f_remote%203-p-500.png 500w, https://assets.website-files.com/5e966657bfb4cd1e103e404b/5edefa0bdc17aa12fc7cf77f_remote%203.png 920w" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 83vw, (max-width: 767px) 360px, (max-width: 991px) 45vw, 37vw" alt="" class="feature-img"/></div></div></div></div></div><div class="section product__features-section"><div class="container"><div class="row product__feature-row reverse-on-sm"><div class="col col-5 col-sm-12"><div data-duration-in="300" data-duration-out="100" class="w-tabs"><div class="w-tab-content"><div data-w-tab="s2-1" class="w-tab-pane w--tab-active"><div class="feature-img-wrapper"><img src="https://assets.website-files.com/5e966657bfb4cd1e103e404b/5edefa103e9039726530c48c_remote%205.png" srcset="https://assets.website-files.com/5e966657bfb4cd1e103e404b/5edefa103e9039726530c48c_remote%205-p-500.png 500w, https://assets.website-files.com/5e966657bfb4cd1e103e404b/5edefa103e9039726530c48c_remote%205.png 920w" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 83vw, (max-width: 767px) 360px, 37vw" alt=""/></div></div><div data-w-tab="s2-2" class="w-tab-pane"><div class="feature-img-wrapper"><img src="https://assets.website-files.com/5e966657bfb4cd1e103e404b/5edefa0df16a5878256d2b3c_remote%206.png" srcset="https://assets.website-files.com/5e966657bfb4cd1e103e404b/5edefa0df16a5878256d2b3c_remote%206-p-500.png 500w, https://assets.website-files.com/5e966657bfb4cd1e103e404b/5edefa0df16a5878256d2b3c_remote%206.png 920w" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 83vw, (max-width: 767px) 360px, 37vw" alt=""/></div></div></div><div class="hidden w-tab-menu"><a data-w-tab="s2-1" class="w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current"><div>Tab 1</div></a><a data-w-tab="s2-2" class="w-inline-block w-tab-link"><